    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Exercices Semaine 1\"\nformat:\n  html:\n    html-math-method: mathjax\n    includes:\n      in_header: |\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n          src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n        </script>\ntoc: false\n\neditor: source\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- JavaScript -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\nfunction toggleAlert(event, message, type) {\n  var alertBox = event.target.nextElementSibling; // Select the alert box next to the clicked button\n  var alertMessage = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertMessage\");\n  var alertType = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertType\");\n\n  if (alertBox.style.display === \"block\") {\n    alertBox.style.display = \"none\"; // Hide the alert box if it's already visible\n  } else {\n    alertMessage.innerHTML = message;\n    alertType.innerHTML = (type === 'hint') ? '‚ùì Indice' : 'üí° Explication';\n\n    // Change style based on type (yellow for hint, green for explanation)\n    alertBox.style.backgroundColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#FFEDA3' : '#C0EDC2';  \n    alertBox.style.borderColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#E5B800' : '#388E3C';  \n    alertBox.style.display = \"block\";  // Show the alert\n\n    MathJax.typesetPromise([alertMessage]);  // Re-render math with MathJax v3\n  }\n}\n</script>\n\n<!-- CSS for Styling -->\n<style>\n/* Custom styles for the buttons */\n.custom-button {\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: black;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.1s ease;\n}\n\n/* Green button for Explanation */\n.explanation {\n  background: #C0EDC2; /* Green */\n  border: 2px solid #388E3C; /* Slightly darker green */\n}\n\n.explanation:hover {\n  background: #388E3C; /* Darker green */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Yellow button for Hint */\n.hint {\n  background: #FFEDA3; /* Yellow */\n  border: 2px solid #E5B800; /* Slightly darker yellow */\n}\n\n.hint:hover {\n  background: #E5B800; /* Darker yellow */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Custom styles for the alert box */\n.alert {\n  padding: 15px;\n  color: black;\n  margin-top: 10px; /* Ensure spacing between button and alert */\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  border: 2px solid;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  width: fit-content; /* Prevent full-width alerts */\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- MathJax for Rendering Math -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n  src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/3.2.2/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n</script>\n\n\n## Question 1\n\nDans une urne contenant \\\\(3\\\\) boules rouges et \\\\(2\\\\) boules bleues, on tire deux boules **avec** remise. Quelle est la probabilit√© d'obtenir deux boules de la m√™me couleur?\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_WFFVXJKUWE'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WFFVXJKUWE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WFFVXJKUWE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WFFVXJKUWE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WFFVXJKUWE\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{52}{100}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Les tirages sont ind√©pendants.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, ' On peut calculer : \\\\(P(RR) = \\\\frac{3}{5}\\\\times\\\\frac{3}{5} \\\\) pour deux rouges \\\\(P(BB) = \\\\frac{2}{5} \\\\times \\\\frac{2}{5} \\\\) pour deux bleues. Ainsi on obtient: \\\\(P(\\\\text{deux boules de la m√™me couleur}) = \\\\frac{9}{25} + \\\\frac{4}{25} = \\\\frac{52}{100}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n## Question 2\n\n\nDans une urne contenant \\\\(3\\\\) boules rouges et \\\\(2\\\\) boules bleues, on tire deux boules **sans** remise. Quelle est la probabilit√© d'obtenir deux boules de la m√™me couleur?\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_WRMIRYOGBX'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WRMIRYOGBX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WRMIRYOGBX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WRMIRYOGBX\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WRMIRYOGBX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Les tirages ne sont pas ind√©pendants.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, ' On peut calculer : \\\\(P(RR) = \\\\frac{3}{5} \\\\times \\\\frac{2}{4} \\\\) pour deux rouges \\\\(P(BB) = \\\\frac{2}{5} \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\) pour deux bleues. Ainsi on obtient: \\\\(P(\\\\text{deux boules de la m√™me couleur}) = \\\\frac{3}{10} + \\\\frac{1}{10} = \\\\frac{4}{10} = \\\\frac{2}{5} \\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 3\n\nSi \\\\( P(A) = \\\\frac{3}{10}\\\\) et \\\\(P(B|A) = \\\\frac{4}{10}\\\\), quelle est la probabilit√© \\\\( P(A \\\\text{ et } B) ? \\\\)\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_OGQRHBIWPL'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OGQRHBIWPL\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{7}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OGQRHBIWPL\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{12}{100}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OGQRHBIWPL\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{10}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_OGQRHBIWPL\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{4}{10}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Les √©v√©nements ne sont pas mutuellement exclusifs.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'En utilisant la r√®gle de multiplication des probabilit√©s : \\\\( P(A \\\\text{ et } B) = P(A) \\\\times P(B|A) =\\\\frac{3}{10} \\\\times \\\\frac{4}{10} = \\\\frac{12}{100} \\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 4\n\nDans une famille ayant trois enfants, quelle est la probabilit√© d'avoir exactement deux filles ?\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_GLWTZSIDJM'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GLWTZSIDJM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{8}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GLWTZSIDJM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GLWTZSIDJM\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{5}{8}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GLWTZSIDJM\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{8}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Listez toutes les configurations possibles.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Sur les \\\\(8\\\\) configurations possibles, \\\\( \\\\{FFF, FFG, FGF, GFF, GGF, GFG, FGG, GGG\\\\} \\\\), il y a exactement \\\\(3\\\\) facons d\\'obtenir \\\\(2\\\\) filles. D\\'o√π la probabilit√© de \\\\(\\\\frac{3}{8}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n## Question 5\n\nLors d'un jeu de cartes avec un paquet classique contenant \\\\(52\\\\) cartes, vous tirez une carte au hasard. Quelle est la probabilit√© que ce soit un roi?\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_GROOXTGRJC'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GROOXTGRJC\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{4}{52}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GROOXTGRJC\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{52}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GROOXTGRJC\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{1}{52}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_GROOXTGRJC\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{8}{52}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Combien y a-t-il de rois dans le paquet?', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Il y a quatre rois dans le paquet (le roi de coeur, de pique, de carreau et de tr√®fle). Ainsi on obtient: \\\\(\\\\frac{4}{52}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 6\n\nLors d'un jeu de cartes avec un paquet classique contenant \\\\(52\\\\) cartes, vous tirez une carte au hasard. Sachant que c'est un roi, quelle est la probabilit√© que ce soit une carte rouge ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_FWMJSIQFBE'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_FWMJSIQFBE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_FWMJSIQFBE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_FWMJSIQFBE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{3}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_FWMJSIQFBE\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Combien y a-t-il de rois rouges dans le paquet?', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Parmi les quatre rois du jeu, exactement deux sont rouges (coeur et carreau) et deux sont noirs (pique et tr√®fle). Donc \\\\(P(\\\\text{Roi rouge} | \\\\text{Roi})\\\\) = \\\\(\\\\frac{2}{4} = \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n## Question 7 \n\nDans une famille avec deux enfants, sachant que l'a√Æn√© est un gar√ßon, quelle est la probabilit√© que les deux enfants soient des gar√ßons ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_CCSEOHOKXG'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CCSEOHOKXG\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CCSEOHOKXG\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CCSEOHOKXG\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{3}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CCSEOHOKXG\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Quelles sont les possibilit√©s si l\\'ain√© est un gar√ßon?', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Sachant que l\\'a√Æn√© est un gar√ßon, notre univers se r√©duit √† \\\\(\\\\{GG, GF\\\\}\\\\). La probabilit√© d\\'avoir un deuxi√®me gar√ßon est donc de \\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n## Question 8\nDans une famille avec deux enfants, sachant qu'au moins l'un des deux est un gar√ßon, quelle est la probabilit√© que les deux enfants soient des gar√ßons ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_ZGKUMMAOLD'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZGKUMMAOLD\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZGKUMMAOLD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZGKUMMAOLD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{3}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZGKUMMAOLD\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Quelles sont les possibilit√©s si l\\'un des deux enfants est un gar√ßon?', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Sachant que l\\'un des deux enfants est un gar√ßon, l\\'univers est \\\\(\\\\{GG, GF, FG\\\\}\\\\). On obtient ainsi \\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 20px;\"></div>\n\n\n\n**Le dilemme de Monty Hall**\n\nUn jeu t√©l√©vis√© propose aux candidats de choisir une porte parmi trois. Derri√®re l'une d'elles se trouve une voiture (le gain), et derri√®re les deux autres, des ch√®vres (perte).\n\nLe candidat choisit une porte au hasard. L‚Äôanimateur (qui sait o√π est la voiture) ouvre ensuite une des deux autres portes pour r√©v√©ler une ch√®vre. Le candidat a alors la possibilit√© de changer de porte ou de conserver son choix initial.\n\n\n## Question 9 \nAvant que l'animateur ouvre une porte, quelle est la probabilit√© que la voiture soit derri√®re la porte initialement choisie par le candidat ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_TDEPAPVBTE'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_TDEPAPVBTE\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_TDEPAPVBTE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_TDEPAPVBTE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_TDEPAPVBTE\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Les √©v√©nements sont √©quiprobables.', 'hint')\">\n  ‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<!-- Button for Explanation -->\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Lorsque le candidat choisit une porte au hasard parmi trois, il y a une probabilit√© √©quiprobable de \\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\) qu\\'il ait choisi la porte avec la voiture derri√®re. En effet, il y a trois portes possibles et une voiture derri√®re une seule porte. La probabilit√© que la voiture soit derri√®re la porte choisie initialement est donc \\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\n  üí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 10\n\nApr√®s que l‚Äôanimateur a ouvert une porte contenant une ch√®vre, quelle est la probabilit√© que la voiture soit derri√®re la porte initialement choisie par le candidat ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_BUMCECNGSJ'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BUMCECNGSJ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BUMCECNGSJ\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BUMCECNGSJ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BUMCECNGSJ\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{3}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Button for Hint -->\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, '√âtant donn√© la probabilit√© i